txt.en: 'The blood I taste when this is done will be yours.'
'Have a little dirt in the eyes!'
*Cough*'I think I can finally taste some blood!'
'My blades will bite deeply as they move like the wind!'
'If you are going to hit me, at least hit me like an Orc!'
Slaughtering my Ongbûrz was a foolish idea.'
